<div id="review_2873021026" class="review nosyndicate" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/2873021026" />
    <a title="Brian " class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/30718608-brian"><img alt="Brian " src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1567218975p2/30718608.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/2873021026?book_show_action=true">Jul 03, 2019</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Brian " class="user" itemprop="url" name="Brian " href="/user/show/30718608-brian">Brian </a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Kindle Edition " href="/book/show/24185349-schismatrix-plus">review of another edition</a>


        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/30718608-brian?shelf=sci-fi">sci-fi</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/30718608-brian?shelf=cyberpunk">cyberpunk</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2873021026" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer14864899689963681579">I enjoyed this! Sterling&apos;s writing style hooked me int he first few pages. I appreciate his literary feel, and his use of drama, and non-typical sci-fi aspects in his novel. The story unfolds over the life of the main character. It&apos;s a future world hooked into computer systems, genetic manipulations and hybrids, aliens, inter-planetary issues, action, mystery, suspense. Although I found the writing difficult to adapt to, I found this a great pleasure. I like his characters. They have depth to me</span>
  <span id="freeText14864899689963681579" style="display:none">I enjoyed this! Sterling's writing style hooked me int he first few pages. I appreciate his literary feel, and his use of drama, and non-typical sci-fi aspects in his novel. The story unfolds over the life of the main character. It's a future world hooked into computer systems, genetic manipulations and hybrids, aliens, inter-planetary issues, action, mystery, suspense. Although I found the writing difficult to adapt to, I found this a great pleasure. I like his characters. They have depth to me. He also describes in detail the workings of the technology, which makes it more believable.</span>
  <a data-text-id="14864899689963681579" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
